nMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529560\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529560\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lgl1665703196282.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lgl1665703196282.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lgl1665703196282.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lgl1665703196282\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Start a number of servers under normal control by the Uniface Router.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_zj4_1yk_gwb\">\n<p class=\"lines\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__lines_rft_gyk_gwb\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">operation START_SERVERS</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">params</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> numeric</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Totalservers</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> : IN ; (I4)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> : IN ; (C40)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> : IN ; (C40)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> : IN ; (C20)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\"> string</code> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Qualifiers</var> <code class=\"ph codeph\"> : IN ; (C256)</code><br/><code class=\"ph codeph\">endparams</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_qd1_myk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d454745e110\">Parameters</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__ul_nk5_nyk_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Totalservers</var>—number of instances of this server to be started. The\n          Uniface Router will not exceed its <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$MAX_SERVERS</span> limit. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">User</var>—user name under which the servers will run. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Password</var>—password for the host machine. <p class=\"p\">The user and password must\n            be a valid combination on the Uniface Router’s host machine.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UST</var>—Uniface Server Type (UST) of the servers. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Qualifiers</var>—optional command line switches to use in starting the\n          servers. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_aqz_4yk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d454745e155\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">If all servers were successfully started, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is set to zero. Be\n        aware that <span class=\"keyword apiname\">START_SERVERS</span> might return an error even though some of the\n        servers were started.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Otherwise, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qln1665702528769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qln1665702528769.html#qln1665702528769__section_fbt_4d2_gwb\">Return Codes</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_hkf_syk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d454745e177\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Allowed in all Uniface component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_yvz_syk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d454745e186\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The privileged-user operation <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">START_SERVERS</span> starts a number of servers\n        under normal Uniface Router control.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__section_iy2_5yk_gwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d454745e199\">Restrictions</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"keyword apiname\">START_SERVERS</span> operation is restricted to privileged users. For more\n        information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vur1665703193539.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vur1665703193539.html\" title=\"Logon as a privileged administrative user of the Uniface Router.\">ADMLOGON</a>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Observe the following restrictions for the UST value and the command line switches:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"lgl1665703196282__ul_dqw_5yk_gwb\">\n<li class=\"li\">If the UST is not specified, the default UST definition will be used, if one exists. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">If the switches you specify conflict with the switches specified in the UST’s definition\n          in the Uniface Router’s assignment file, the values in the assignment file take\n          precedence. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">If the UST you enter matches a specific or a default UST definition, you may not use the\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dir</span> and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/asn</span> switches. Otherwise, these switches\n          and the switches <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dnp</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ex</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/shr</span>,\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/su</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">-nosu</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/pri</span>, and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/drv</span> may be used. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">You may not specify the UST using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/ust</span> switch. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">You may not use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/max</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/maxidle</span>, and\n            <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/maxreq</span> switches. </li>\n<li class=\"li\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/drv</span> switch determines the type of server to be started, for\n          example, ORA for an Oracle database server, FIL for a file server, or S3C for a Uniface\n          Application Server. If the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/drv</span> switch is not specified, it defaults to\n          the ANY server. For a database server, you may not specify the database user name and\n          password; they will be determined by the first client request assigned to the server.\n        </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529560\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529560\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "START_SERVERS Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Start a number of servers under normal control by the Uniface Router. operation START_SERVERS params numeric Totalservers : IN ; (I4) string User : IN ; (C40) string Password : IN ; (C40) string UST : IN ; (C20) string Qualifiers : IN ; (C256) endparams Parameters Totalservers —number of instances of this server to be started. The Uniface Router will not exceed its $MAX_SERVERS limit. User —user name under which the servers will run. Password —password for the host machine. The user and password must be a valid combination on the Uniface Router’s host machine. UST —Uniface Server Type (UST) of the servers. Qualifiers —optional command line switches to use in starting the servers. Return Values If all servers were successfully started, $status is set to zero. Be aware that START_SERVERS might return an error even though some of the servers were started. Otherwise, see Return Codes . Use Allowed in all Uniface component types. Description The privileged-user operation START_SERVERS starts a number of servers under normal Uniface Router control. Restrictions The START_SERVERS operation is restricted to privileged users. For more information, see ADMLOGON . Observe the following restrictions for the UST value and the command line switches: If the UST is not specified, the default UST definition will be used, if one exists. If the switches you specify conflict with the switches specified in the UST’s definition in the Uniface Router’s assignment file, the values in the assignment file take precedence. If the UST you enter matches a specific or a default UST definition, you may not use the /dir and /asn switches. Otherwise, these switches and the switches /dnp , /ex , /shr , /su , -nosu , /pri , and /drv may be used. You may not specify the UST using the /ust switch. You may not use the /max , /maxidle , and /maxreq switches. The /drv switch determines the type of server to be started, for example, ORA for an Oracle database server, FIL for a file server, or S3C for a Uniface Application Server. If the /drv switch is not specified, it defaults to the ANY server. For a database server, you may not specify the database user name and password; they will be determined by the first client request assigned to the server. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}